683
01:17:00,215 --> 01:17:01,216
Con gusto.

684
01:17:06,763 --> 01:17:08,849
¡Zorro, Balto, vamos!

685
01:17:25,490 --> 01:17:26,491
Ven conmigo.

686
01:17:27,117 --> 01:17:28,326
No tengo tiempo.

687
01:17:29,036 --> 01:17:30,078
Ven.

688
01:17:30,162 --> 01:17:31,455
Tengo que irme.

689
01:17:40,213 --> 01:17:41,965
